The paper discusses knowledge extraction and query expansion, which are common topics in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of Wikipedia as a knowledge base also suggests a connection to databases (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the analysis of graph structures could also be relevant to machine learning (cs.LG).
